\int_{-\infty}^\infty \frac{x\sin(\omega x)}{x^4+1}\,dx
\frac{1}{i}\int_{-\infty}^\infty \frac{xe^{\omega i x}}{x^4+1}\,dx
(-a,a)
0
i
e^{ix} = \cos(x)+i\sin(x)
\int_{-\infty}^\infty \frac{xe^{\omega i x}}{x^4+1}dx = \int_{-\infty}^\infty \frac{x(\cos(\omega x) + i\sin(\omega x))}{x^4+1}dx =\int_{-\infty}^\infty \frac{x\cos(\omega x)}{x^4+1}dx+\int_{-\infty}^\infty \frac{i\sin(\omega x)}{x^4+1}dx
\int_{-\infty}^\infty \frac{xe^{\omega i x}}{x^4+1}dx = i\int_{-\infty}^\infty \frac{\sin(\omega x)}{x^4+1}dx
